    "description": "该模板是GameCreator官方出品的游戏模板-《空之跃》。 是一款无任何自带战斗系统的平台跳跃游戏模板。<br>该模板包含了GameCreator引擎的功能以及模板独有的核心系统以及编辑器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用难度</h2>★★<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏手柄和SteamDeck支持</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/5e714d2cd9e04cdd203a874cd80dbf7f.avif?t=1742051865\" width=620 height=272 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心功能</h2>以下是部分功能效果演示<br><br>● 自研的轻量级物理系统：重力、移动、多段跳跃、冲刺、攀爬等等<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/1fe7cf724feece9c9224d4a09e59fd4c.poster.avif?t=1742051865\" width=576 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/1fe7cf724feece9c9224d4a09e59fd4c.webm?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/1fe7cf724feece9c9224d4a09e59fd4c.mp4?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>● 水世界，在水中拥有额外的阻力<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/9f6a17493dd8e0f35fdcff4d46bd1dff.poster.avif?t=1742051865\" width=576 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/9f6a17493dd8e0f35fdcff4d46bd1dff.webm?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/9f6a17493dd8e0f35fdcff4d46bd1dff.mp4?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>● 攀爬能力，可以制作在拾取相关道具后拥有攀爬的能力<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/bbebafcc1639a3169902b53f0797cffc.poster.avif?t=1742051865\" width=576 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/bbebafcc1639a3169902b53f0797cffc.webm?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/bbebafcc1639a3169902b53f0797cffc.mp4?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>● 传送带与推动物体<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/a9943a111a6450c2f8e0874c1dafdc7a.poster.avif?t=1742051865\" width=576 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/a9943a111a6450c2f8e0874c1dafdc7a.webm?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/a9943a111a6450c2f8e0874c1dafdc7a.mp4?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>● 隐藏块：当碰触后才会显现<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/163f75529ad6324618166c062496446a.poster.avif?t=1742051865\" width=576 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/163f75529ad6324618166c062496446a.webm?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/163f75529ad6324618166c062496446a.mp4?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>● 钥匙、锁、开关按钮<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/f0aa8d7a3d29945316e6d7cc3925c423.poster.avif?t=1742051865\" width=576 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/f0aa8d7a3d29945316e6d7cc3925c423.webm?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/f0aa8d7a3d29945316e6d7cc3925c423.mp4?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>● 运动块载物<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/4bcc16645bc8dfbc069ed24bd91f319d.poster.avif?t=1742051865\" width=576 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/4bcc16645bc8dfbc069ed24bd91f319d.webm?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331200/extras/4bcc16645bc8dfbc069ed24bd91f319d.mp4?t=1742051865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>● 冰块：当停止移动后会有额外的惯性，使人物滑动<br>● 减速块：站在减速块上时移动会更缓慢<br>● 弹力块：碰触后会往让玩家往某个方向弹开<br>● 条件块：拾取指定道具后这些条件块会自动消失<br>● 陷阱：碰到陷阱后角色会死亡<br>● 禁止跳跃块：站在禁止跳跃块上面无法跳跃<br>● 跳跃刷新块：碰触跳跃刷新块后跳跃次数将会被刷新，允许再次跳跃<br>● 消失块：站在消失块上，该块会逐渐消失，然后一段时间后自动出现<br>● 感应块：感应到玩家的跳跃行为，每次跳跃后消失或出现<br>● 传送块：可以传送到指定的坐标或者场景上<br>● 指示牌：接触指示牌后可显示预设的提示文字<br>● 存档块：碰触后可以立刻存档<br>● 多种道具：如钥匙、金币、多段跳跃道具、冲刺道具、攀爬道具、变身道具等等<br>● 更多特性，待您体验！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模板的使用方式</h2>● 将图块绘制在地图上制作地形<br><br>● 将功能块摆放到地图上<br>● 启动游戏<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高级扩展</h2>● 通过触发器与力模块允许可视化实现各种物理效果（如攀爬、传送带等各种功能块都是）<br><br>● 行走图允许逐帧设计包围盒，让其在播放时动态更改碰撞体积<br>● 高级开发者可以修改和扩展脚本程序以及制作插件<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于素材利用规则</h2>● 模板内置素材允许商用。<br><br>● 如用于非GameCreator引擎则需要购买专业版的GC软件且注明来源 。<br>● 不允许转售稍微修改的素材版本，但允许免费分享且必须与该规则相同。",
